Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:04.87,Hifumi,Hifumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.95,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hai detto qualcosa Hifumi?
