Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:52.15,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Abbiamo nascosto la vista e i rumori piuttosto bene, ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.86,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Come sei sciocco.
