Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:42.21,Hifumi,Hifumi,0000,0000,0000,,Cosa c'è?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:44.55,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Hifumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:48.84,Hifumi,Hifumi,0000,0000,0000,,Perché sei nervosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:51.51,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Non dobbiamo fare come l'ultima volta?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:54.27,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Mi sento molto meglio del solito.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:57.14,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Quindi ho pensato che potrebbe essere piacevole farlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:01.15,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hifumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:03.36,Hifumi,Hifumi,0000,0000,0000,,Perché a me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:05.36,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Cosa? Perché?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:08.99,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Non è piacevole per una ragazza questo genere di rifiuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:10.99,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Mi stai ascoltando?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:14.37,Hifumi,Hifumi,0000,0000,0000,,Non dovrebbe essere così, ma più...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:26.34,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Che dolce brezza.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:52.95,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,E' profondo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:59.16,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Mi piace il tuo cazzo così in profondità...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.60,0:24:17.72,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,E' profondo e molto ruvido...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.02,0:24:27.40,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hifumi-kun, questo no..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.34,0:24:49.26,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Dammelo Hifumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:51.80,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Vieni dentro di me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.37,0:25:24.00,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hifumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.75,0:25:25.75,Hifumi,Hifumi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.83,0:25:26.88,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Lo sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.00,0:25:27.96,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Cosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.04,0:25:32.34,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Mi piaci tantissimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.76,0:25:33.55,Hifumi,Hifumi,0000,0000,0000,,Stupida.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.67,0:25:36.68,Hifumi,Hifumi,0000,0000,0000,,E ora io come potrei risponderti?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.35,0:25:39.35,Hifumi,Hifumi,0000,0000,0000,,Cosa dia-
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.68,0:25:43.39,Fuwari,Fuwari,0000,0000,0000,,Se non le dici quello che provi con parole tue...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.52,0:25:46.35,Fuwari,Fuwari,0000,0000,0000,,...ti faremo sentire una nullità e ti getteremo in una discarica.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.52,0:25:47.36,Hirari,Hirari,0000,0000,0000,,E' giusto.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.48,0:25:49.77,Hirari,Hirari,0000,0000,0000,,Sei sempre stato maldestro fin da piccolino.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.90,0:25:51.48,Hirari,Hirari,0000,0000,0000,,Sono un po' preoccupata per te.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.40,0:25:56.36,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Non ti piaccio Hifumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.11,0:25:59.53,Hifumi,Hifumi,0000,0000,0000,,Cosa? Cosa? Cosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.20,0:26:03.29,Hifumi,Hifumi,0000,0000,0000,,Non si può!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.37,0:26:05.79,Kaede,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Cosa?
